name: Geocoder
tagline: Geocodes addresses from a CSV file and only returns those addresses that have a single non-partial result and that have a geocode that is of "ROOFTOP" quality.
body:
geocoder
========

Geocodes addresses from a CSV file and only returns those addresses that have a single non-partial result and that have a geocode that is of "ROOFTOP" quality.
